            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Malachi.1:1-2:17",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EMalachi%201%3A1-2%3A17%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EMalachi%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Oracle%3A%20The%20message.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20gave%20to%20Israel%20through%20the%20prophet%20Malachi.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A1b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cem%3EMalachi%3C%2Fem%3E%20means%20%26%23x201C%3Bmy%20messenger.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Love%20for%20Israel%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20always%20loved%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EBut%20you%20retort%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BReally%3F%20How%20have%20you%20loved%20us%3F%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EAnd%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20replies%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20how%20I%20showed%20my%20love%20for%20you%3A%20I%20loved%20your%20ancestor%20Jacob%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3Ebut%20I%20rejected%20his%20brother%2C%20Esau%2C%20and%20devastated%20his%20hill%20country.%20I%20turned%20Esau%26%23x2019%3Bs%20inheritance%20into%20a%20desert%20for%20jackals.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EEsau%26%23x2019%3Bs%20descendants%20in%20Edom%20may%20say%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWe%20have%20been%20shattered%2C%20but%20we%20will%20rebuild%20the%20ruins.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3EBut%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20replies%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BThey%20may%20try%20to%20rebuild%2C%20but%20I%20will%20demolish%20them%20again.%20Their%20country%20will%20be%20known%20as%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20Land%20of%20Wickedness%2C%26%23x2019%3B%20and%20their%20people%20will%20be%20called%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20People%20with%20Whom%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Is%20Forever%20Angry.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20you%20see%20the%20destruction%20for%20yourselves%2C%20you%20will%20say%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BTruly%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20greatness%20reaches%20far%20beyond%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20borders!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EUnworthy%20Sacrifices%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20says%20to%20the%20priests%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BA%20son%20honors%20his%20father%2C%20and%20a%20servant%20respects%20his%20master.%20If%20I%20am%20your%20father%20and%20master%2C%20where%20are%20the%20honor%20and%20respect%20I%20deserve%3F%20You%20have%20shown%20contempt%20for%20my%20name!%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20you%20ask%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BHow%20have%20we%20ever%20shown%20contempt%20for%20your%20name%3F%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20have%20shown%20contempt%20by%20offering%20defiled%20sacrifices%20on%20my%20altar.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThen%20you%20ask%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BHow%20have%20we%20defiled%20the%20sacrifices%3F%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3Edefiled%20you%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BYou%20defile%20them%20by%20saying%20the%20altar%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20deserves%20no%20respect.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20you%20give%20blind%20animals%20as%20sacrifices%2C%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20that%20wrong%3F%20And%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20it%20wrong%20to%20offer%20animals%20that%20are%20crippled%20and%20diseased%3F%20Try%20giving%20gifts%20like%20that%20to%20your%20governor%2C%20and%20see%20how%20pleased%20he%20is!%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20ahead%2C%20beg%20God%20to%20be%20merciful%20to%20you!%20But%20when%20you%20bring%20that%20kind%20of%20offering%2C%20why%20should%20he%20show%20you%20any%20favor%20at%20all%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20asks%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHow%20I%20wish%20one%20of%20you%20would%20shut%20the%20Temple%20doors%20so%20that%20these%20worthless%20sacrifices%20could%20not%20be%20offered!%20I%20am%20not%20pleased%20with%20you%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%2C%20%26%23x201C%3Band%20I%20will%20not%20accept%20your%20offerings.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20my%20name%20is%20honored%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A11a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ewill%20be%20honored.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20people%20of%20other%20nations%20from%20morning%20till%20night.%20All%20around%20the%20world%20they%20offer%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A11b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ewill%20offer.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20sweet%20incense%20and%20pure%20offerings%20in%20honor%20of%20my%20name.%20For%20my%20name%20is%20great%20among%20the%20nations%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20says%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22mala_1_12%22%20bk%3D%22mala%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3